coder v0.0.0-devel

USAGE:
  coder users edit-roles [flags] <username|user_id>

  Edit a user's roles by username or id

OPTIONS:
      --add string-array
          A list of roles to add to the user's existing roles. Cannot be used
          together with --roles.

      --remove string-array
          A list of roles to remove from the user's existing roles. Cannot be
          used together with --roles.

      --roles string-array
          A list of roles to give to the user. This removes any existing roles
          the user may have.

  -y, --yes bool
          Bypass confirmation prompts.

———
Run `coder --help` for a list of global options.
